snippet.textDisplay: I played through this game with a friend and it was really fun. I guess it must be even better with 3 other friends. It has fun graphics, great music and a good variety of characters and weapons. I thought the combat system was a bit stale by the end of the game though, lacking more moves and combos. My main character was the Green Knight, loved him!
